1282
01:14:02.521 --> 01:14:06.108
I've...
I've made my choice.

1283
01:14:07.276 --> 01:14:11.196
I'm choosing the...
other reality over this one.

1284
01:14:12.448 --> 01:14:13.949
I'm going to make it permanent.

1285
01:14:16.243 --> 01:14:17.453
There's a...

1286
01:14:18.579 --> 01:14:20.873
There's a taxi
