1322
01:17:02.326 --> 01:17:04.244
Why? What happens?

1323
01:17:04.828 --> 01:17:07.289
I don't know
how to put this. I guess...

1324
01:17:11.335 --> 01:17:13.086
There's some shit
that's about to come down

1325
