1326
01:17:16.423 --> 01:17:19.926
An enemy's coming that has
no weakness cannot be stopped.

1327
01:17:19.968 --> 01:17:22.471
and outnumbers us at minimum.
ten to one.

1328
01:17:22.512 --> 01:17:24.056
