1336
01:17:45.369 --> 01:17:47.788
-They spread disease.
-Yeah. that's right. Mark.

1337
01:17:47.829 --> 01:17:49.956
- Another time fire.
- Oh my God.

1338
01:17:49.998 --> 01:17:52.793
