1356
01:18:30.122 --> 01:18:33.375
Why can't it be something cool?
Like... a centaur?

1357
01:18:33.417 --> 01:18:34.626
-Oh!
-Okay. Stop!

1358
01:18:34.668 --> 01:18:35.961
