1360
01:18:37.671 --> 01:18:38.922
Just throwing confetti.

1361
01:18:38.964 --> 01:18:41.007
-They just make us happy.
-They make us happy.

1362
01:18:41.049 --> 01:18:43.552
Just make you happy. huh? Yeah.

1363
