1472
01:28:20.003 --> 01:28:22.255
Well. I started this
and I'm going to finish it.

1473
01:28:22.297 --> 01:28:23.589
What are you talking about?

1474
01:28:23.631 --> 01:28:25.675
There's no way you're
gonna make it to the house

1475
01:28:25.717 --> 01:28:29.887
